articles.title: 25 people killed in Gaza as Gaza City becomes the focus of famine and a military offensive
articles.description: Hospital officials in Gaza say Israeli strikes and gunfire have killed at least 25 Palestinians sheltering in tents or seeking scarce food aid [4].
